  },
  {
    question: "Can you clean large homes in Hampton Cove and The Ledges?",
    answer: "Absolutely! We regularly clean large estate homes in Hampton Cove, The Ledges, Monte Sano, and Jones Valley. Our team is experienced with high-end finishes, multiple bathrooms, large kitchens, and the attention to detail these premium properties require."
  },
  {
    question: "How far in advance should I schedule move-out cleaning?",
