  },
  {
    question: "What if the previous tenant left the home very dirty?",
    answer: "We can handle heavily soiled properties, though pricing may be adjusted for extreme conditions. Let us know the situation when requesting a quote, and we'll provide an accurate estimate. Before-and-after photos help us assess the scope and provide fair pricing."
  },
