    question: "Can you accommodate move-out cleaning for Research Park and Bridge Street area condos?",
    answer: "Yes — high-rise condos, mid-rise buildings, and condo communities throughout the Research Park, Bridge Street, and Downtown Huntsville corridors are served by our move-out cleaning service. These properties often have HOA cleaning standards in addition to lease cleaning requirements, and we understand both layers. Building access, elevator scheduling, and parking logistics for cleaning services in these buildings are details we navigate as standard procedure for urban Huntsville properties."
  },
  {
    question: "What's your satisfaction guarantee for Huntsville move-out cleaning?",
    answer: "If your property manager or housing inspector identifies any cleaning issue within our scope during their inspection, call us within 72 hours and we'll return to correct it at no charge. No forms, no complicated process. We stand behind our Huntsville move-out cleaning completely. Our goal is a passed inspection on the first walkthrough — and if something is found, we return and fix it. This guarantee is backed by our $2 million liability insurance and our years of serving Madison County renters and military families."
  }
];

// Schema markup
const serviceSchema = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "Service",
